dct_title_s: Map of the forest reserves of California
dct_description_sm: compiled by the State Mining Bureau, Ferry Building, San Francisco, from data published by the U.S. Forest Service.
Shows established and proposed forest reserves, National Parks, railways, drainage, and township and range grid.
Includes list of forests and area covered.
